---
import Portrait from '../assets/portrait.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="About Me"
	pubDate={new Date('April 6 2026')}
	heroImage={Portrait}
	heroImageAlt="Mt Bierstadt Summit"
>
	<p>
		Self-taught, 10+ years building full-stack APIs.
		Lately I've been dragging myself closer to the metal — embedded systems, sensor drivers, microcontrollers.
		I've written some SPI drivers, battled LED matrix displays, and I'm always mid-way through <s>three</s> five projects at once.
		If it involves figuring out how something actually works under the hood (or has enough LEDs), I'm probably interested.
		Outside of code: skiing, hiking, motorcycles, reading, sim games.
	</p>
</Layout>
